        "note": "AIP closes this boundary via 'along HCM/Singapore FIR bdry - along HCM/Manila FIR bdry (114E) - crossing pt lat 14 42'12\"N - along that latitude - DONDA - EXOTO - D05'. UPDATED: DONDA (112.021667E, 14.703333N) and EXOTO (111.05E, 15.358333N) coordinates, previously missing, are now available from VV-ENR-4_4-en.pdf and have been inserted verbatim, replacing the earlier D08->crossing pt->D05 two-segment stand-in with D08->crossing pt->DONDA->EXOTO->D05. Confidence raised low->medium accordingly. The remaining approximation is the D08->crossing-point jog itself: the AIP describes this only as 'along HCM/Singapore FIR boundary, then along HCM/Manila FIR boundary', with no vertex list for that FIR-boundary polyline in any supplied extract, so it is still rendered as a single straight segment rather than the real (multi-vertex) boundary line.",
